'''泛东南亚日本海底光缆系统'''（{{lang|en|South-East Asia Japan Cable System}}，简称：'''SJC'''）是一组连接泛东南亚（东亚及东南亚）地区的海底光缆网络，连接登陆点包括日本、中国大陆、香港、菲律宾、文莱、泰国、新加坡及印尼。<ref>{{cite web |title=South-East Asia Japan Cable System (SJC) |url=http://submarinenetworks.com/systems/intra-asia/sjc |publisher=Submarine Cable Networks |accessdate=24 March 2014 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225175912/https://www.submarinenetworks.com/systems/intra-asia/sjc |dead-url=no }}</ref>该光缆使用6对光缆，初始设定容量可提供每秒15T[[位元|bit]]的通信流量，最高可升级至每秒23Tbit，<ref name="iccsz">{{cite web|title=全面解读全球海底光缆发展及我国海缆分布概况 - 讯石光通讯网-做光通讯行业的充电站!|url=http://www.iccsz.com/site/cn/News/2015/06/30/20150630035544316214.htm|access-date=2015-07-09|archive-date=2015-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716090933/http://www.iccsz.com/site/cn/News/2015/06/30/20150630035544316214.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>使用40G SLTE及{{tsl|en|Optical_add-drop_multiplexer|光分插复用}}技术。<ref>{{cite web|title=TE Subcom completes first 40g upgrade of a trans-Pacific cable system {{!}} DataCentres.com|url=http://www.datacentres.com/news/te-subcom-completes-first-40g-upgrade-trans-pacific-cable-system|access-date=2015-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150716100421/http://www.datacentres.com/news/te-subcom-completes-first-40g-upgrade-trans-pacific-cable-system|archive-date=2015-07-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=South-East Asia Japan Cable (SJC) System Consortium Contracts with SubCom and NEC as Suppliers: News: Submarine Systems: Networking: Products {{!}} NEC|url=http://www.nec.com/en/global/prod/nw/submarine/news/2011/20110412.html|access-date=2015-07-09|archive-date=2016-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309211458/http://www.nec.com/en/global/prod/nw/submarine/news/2011/20110412.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>该网络于2013年6月27日启用。

